lead_paragraph: Top-seeded Roger Federer cruised in the tiebreakers to beat German qualifier Florian Mayer 7-6 (2), 7-6 (1) for a place in the Mercedes Cup semifinals on Friday.

headline.print_headline: Federer Beats Mayer to Set Up Semifinal With Thiem
